Read the implementation spec at `.hanness/pages/page_04_card_rendering.page` and implement everything described.

Prerequisites: page_01 (CardDefs, CardStack) must be complete.

Steps:
1. Create `client/src/ui/StackBadge.js` — circle + text, hidden when count <= 1.
2. Create `client/src/ui/CardSprite.js` — Phaser3 Container with background, icon, label, badge, timer text.
3. Apply category-based background colors from the CAT_COLOR table in the spec.
4. Implement refresh(timeNow) to update badge count and countdown timer.
5. Implement setHighlight(on) and setDragging(on).
6. Add sprite pool management helpers (addCardSprite, refreshSprites) to GameScene.

After implementing, verify each acceptance criterion listed at the bottom of the spec.
